summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; adding a new Section 23.53.035 regarding structural building overhangs to the Seattle Municipal Code and amending Sections 23.22.062, 23.24.045, 23.44.016, 23.44.080, 23.49.212, 23.76.004, 23.76.006, and 23.84.024 of the Seattle Municipal Code to clarify code provisions, correct oversights, errors and omissions, and to make certain substantive amendments.
